com.axeda.toolkit.ammp.domain
Class Event

java.lang.Object
  com.axeda.toolkit.ammp.domain.Event
All Implemented Interfaces:
com.axeda.toolkit.util.json.JSONSerializer
public class Event
extends Object
implements com.axeda.toolkit.util.json.JSONSerializer

Representation of an AMMP Event. All instances are immutable and are constructed via the Event.Builder class. The following example creates an Event with optional acquisitionTime and priority. 

 
      Event event = new Event.Builder("Event name", "Event description")
                            .acquisitionTime(new java.util.Date())
                            .priority(100)
                            .build();
